<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_247" id="122r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_247_r3l26"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> am Samſʒtag vor Maria Magdalene . die erſten naht cʒu Ẏgelſtorff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r3l27"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> am Suntag . / Montag . Eritag vnd Mitvvochen cʒu Hẏrſheyde / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r3l28"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> von Hirſheẏde gen der Heẏde / da lag man v tag / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_line_1571050246899_142"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> am Montag gen Probach . <expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>t<ex>er</ex>tia</expan> et <expan>q<ex>ua</ex>rta</expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> in holcʒhawſen . / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r3l31"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>q<ex>ui</ex>nta</expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> in Eybſtalt . <expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ſexta in dem velde bey Mellerſtat . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_line_1571050270424_157">vnd bey <hi rend="underlined">Roſʒried </hi> viij tag . / <expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ſexta . Nẏderlawer / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_line_1571050285459_165"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> cʒu Ranfelt . / <expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> am Suntag / cʒu Herrhaim vnd Montag / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r3l34">am Eritag cʒu Fürerſe / <expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> am Mitvvochen cʒu Oberlinteich </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_247" id="122r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> am <app><note><q type="date">samsztag vor Maria Magdalene</q>20.07.1409</note></app> die ersten naht
        czu Ygelstorff. <lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> am <app><note><q type="date">suntag, montag, eritag
            und mitwochen</q>21.-24.07.1409</note></app> czu Hyrsheyde. <lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> von Hirsheyde
        gen der heyde da lag man v tag. <lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> am <app><note><q type="date">montag</q>29.07.1409</note></app>
                        gen Probach. <expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>t<ex>er</ex>tia</expan> et <expan>q<ex>ua</ex>rta</expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan></q>30./31.07.1409</note></app> in Holczhawsen.
                            <lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>q<ex>ui</ex>nta</expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan></q>01.08.1409</note></app> in Eybstalt. <lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> sexta</q>02.08.1409</note></app> in dem velde bey Mellerstat und bey <hi rend="underlined">Roszried </hi> viii tag.
                            <expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> sexta</q>09.08.1409</note></app> nyderlawer.
                            <lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan></q>10.08.1409</note></app> czu Ranfelt.
        <lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> am <app><note><q type="date">suntag</q>11.08.1409</note></app> czu Herrhaim und <app><note><q type="date">montag</q>12.08.1409</note></app> am
        <app><note><q type="date">eritag</q>13.08.1409</note></app> czu Fürerse. <expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> am <app><note><q type="date">mitwochen</q>14.08.1409</note></app> czu
                        Oberlinteich. </ab>
</div>
